{"tid":1993813,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"以為「投資」可以透過報 course 學得識，真心好笑","createTime":"2020-04-29T04:49:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T12:01:33.000Z","uid":123335,"like":66,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"9e5d809755c2c1fb4d0f107946ebbb3b80a07d47","tid":1993813,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:49:28.000Z","msg":"有班新手 <br />\n以為報果d 萬幾蚊既 投資 course <br />\n就可以入股場中撈返一大筆<br />\n繼而邁向財務自由<br />\n呢堆人係最on9 <br />\n真係笑都廢事 <br />\n<br />\n另一批新手<br />\n稍為好少少，會選擇喺書局買入門投資書<br />\n學習成本相對低，亦學到唔少野 <br />\n睇完幾本入門書，<br />\n包括《漫步華爾街》、《巴菲特給股東的信》...etc<br />\n就會開始心雄，以超越巴菲特為目標 <br />\n往往會掛住「價值投資」係嘴邊<br />\n結果都係俾股市撚到輸錢<br />\n大嗌「騙局！」<br />\n<br />\n其實股市冇你想像中咁正路<br />\n佢的確有自己既一套 rule <br />\n要你親身落場去學 <br />\n<br />\n坦白講，你睇書、報course 學到果d <br />\n已經係56k 年代既產物 <br />\n家陣5G都黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f00b3465acf64b8c17aab2ad9c9f1acf9425eb0","tid":1993813,"uid":299792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:49:44.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"2e393c664b3d79b798d95d43d6eecbfc55b74364","tid":1993813,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:50:08.000Z","msg":"彪哥 好掛住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf0891b19a7783e0189d6f54339cb2a9e530bb30","tid":1993813,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e393c664b3d79b798d95d43d6eecbfc55b74364","tid":1993813,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:50:08.000Z","msg":"彪哥 好掛住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:50:38.000Z","msg":"搞乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾日冇開post 姐"},{"pid":"74039acb00c9